        h4 About me
        p.light My name is Jacob Zimmerman, I'm 19 years old, and I love calling New Berlin, Wisconsin home. I currently attend Carnegie Mellon University studing Computer Science as a part of the class of 2017 (with hopes of graduating sooner!).
        p.light I spend my free time (wait... that doesn't sound right) making cool things and trying to help other people make cooler things. I'm pretty good with a yo-yo, and I love playing ping-pong and tennis (when it's not snowing outside).
        p.light I prefer wielding Java, JavaScript, HTML/CSS, and Node.js, but I've also worked in C, C++, Python, and a few others. I pick things up pretty quickly too: everything you see here I've learned since I got to CMU less than 6 months ago. I always love trying out new techniques and taking risks.
